.TH fetchmailmond 1 "@PACKAGE@ @VERSION@"
.SH NAME
fetchmailmond \- fetchmail monitor daemon
.SH SYNOPSIS
.BI "fetchmailmond [-vdhV] [--session] [file]"
.sp
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B fetchmailmond
daemon monitors the log produced by
.B fetchmail
to distribute this information to clients.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\-v, \--version
Show version informations and terminate.
.TP
\-h, \--help
Show help (usage) and terminate.
.TP
\-d, \--debug
Enable debug output.
.TP
\-V, \--vebose
Enable verbose output.
.TP
\--session
Use the session bus (instead of system bus).
.TP
\--session
Use the session bus (instead of system bus).
.TP
file
Monitor this file instead of default one (@DEFAULT_MAILLOG_FILENAME@).

.SH FILES
.TP
@DEFAULT_MAILLOG_FILENAME@
The default system messages file read.

.SH "SEE ALSO"
.BR fetchmail (1),
.BR dbus-daemon (1)

